  <description><![CDATA[<p>Situated in a sunny position in <a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a> this hotel brings friendly service from your hosts, the Baud family, as well as a wide range of facilities including a lovely spa area with Hamman, sauna and whirlpool. Relax in the hotels outdoor heated swimming pool, looking out over the picturesque mountains or alternatively, pamper yourself with a treatment from the spa.</p>
<p>Located in the heart of the old town, this property is only 3 minutes from the centre, allowing you the freedom to wander and enjoy the village's lovely atmosphere.</p>
<p>Return after a day of exploring the mountains to a drink in front of the fire in the lounge and bar area, before enjoying your three course evening meal in the Savoyard restaurant. Awarded the title of "Maitre Restaurateur" this hotel provides excellent regional cuisine and specialities, all of which are created from fresh produce only.</p>
<p>The rooms are all furnished with a traditional Alpine theme, with each one having a private balcony that overlooks the lush green mountain landscape.</p>]]></description>
