  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking), bath with shower head attachment or shower room, WC, hair dryer, telephone, safe, cable / satellite flat screen TV with English speaking channels, mini bar, tea and coffee making facilities, WiFi and a balcony with mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Double/Twin Rooms</strong> sleep 2 people (22m²). Also available for sole occupancy.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep 3-4 people (35m²). Additional double sofa bed suitable for children up to 11 years.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Family Rooms</strong> sleep 3-4 people (40m²). Additional double sofa bed suitable for children up to 11 years.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> sleep 2-4 (40m²). Bedroom with double bed and separate living area with double sofa bed.</p>
<p>Please call to book the Family Rooms and Junior Suites</p>]]></roomsDescription>
